	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Dunno. I'm gonna purchase an assembled one from him, but no idea if he's gonna offer them built to order or not. 
<br />
<br /> I did receive some more info from him:
<br />
<br /> CS0 and CS1 areas are 256k segments each. And you can use a single 256k sram IC on each, for a total of 512k ram in the upper 8megabit range. He just has a standard setup where 128k is on one (mirrored) and 8k fram on the other (mirrored too). Or put an audio upgrade IC on either of them. Etc.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


